{"tid":2312424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全面脫貧+內循環+大灣區= 幾雞1餐、幾草叫雞  中国「天堂」","createTime":"2020-12-05T02:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T10:18:12.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"734043082ccf9ec355046b380598b6b772a972ff","tid":2312424,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T02:50:23.000Z","msg":"現代年輕人起薪不高，生活大不易，不僅職業倦怠，甚至對世界感到厭世；中國就有一群人放棄生計、身份、尊嚴，在繁華的城市角落打造出一處「墮落天堂」。<br />\n<br />\n距離深圳市中心不到10公里的龍華新區，有個名叫三和人才市場的地方，一群被稱作「三和大神」的青年長期在該處遊蕩，他們崇尚「及時行樂」，只要打工賺到幾百元，就立刻把錢花在網咖、買春，貫徹「做1玩3」的守則。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/04/2918872-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F04%2F2918872-PH.jpg&h=7dd88f35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《網易新聞》報導，「三和大神」秉持打零工、日結精神，只要賺到百來元後，便開始實踐「吃喝嫖賭抽」5字真訣；儘管物價近年節節攀升，然而在三和，生活成本幾乎被壓縮到極限，只要花上人民幣2元（約新台幣8元）就能吃到1份腸粉，若多花個1元，還可以來上1碗熱騰騰的青菜湯麵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/04/2918873-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F04%2F2918873-PH.jpg&h=bc5650f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吃飽喝足後，三和大神們有些會到網咖，每小時1.5元（約新台幣6元），花上8元（約新台幣34元）就能玩通宵，累了便直接在座位上睡覺；也有些人則會到市場附近的龍華公園裡「發洩」，報導指出，該處暗藏著大批應召女子，只要30至50元（約新台幣130元至215元）就可以潦草地解決性需求。<br />\n<br />\n隨著口袋見底，大神們索性以天為被、地為席，在海信人力資源市場外就地躺平，直到餓昏，才會起身找尋下一份臨時工；而不少人則是連打工都不想，靠著賣血、手機、身分證換取微薄收入，最後甚至淪落到翻垃圾桶維生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=859878\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D859878&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w6hYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=defe096f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D859878&h=56eabfd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=859878</a>"},{"pid":"5fe9b92429eb61f4c9cb19d1355459fa44d818b2","tid":2312424,"uid":25260,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T02:53:11.000Z","msg":"Fake news <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n習大大明明話全面脫貧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c4c89ef3e3e8d4e969a7986f5307ae9583bc05","tid":2312424,"uid":213111,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T02:53:45.000Z","msg":"fake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff0079f7bf76284e9f50d58026c0670b8320e1d","tid":2312424,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T03:23:57.000Z","msg":"三和沒落左啦  出名果幾間散工都執左<br />\n應該係唔可以咁揚 冇以前咁集中"},{"pid":"d29d6ba1998c8f3592043a97fdc5e78f81cada5e","tid":2312424,"uid":325118,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T03:26:34.000Z","msg":"群雞起舞，我要幾十個老雞服侍我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5266221dc9b5d70abcc2bc6985afe0db6a10acac","tid":2312424,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b75317113940fe05c31d17575950956097053fc","tid":2312424,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d29d6ba1998c8f3592043a97fdc5e78f81cada5e","tid":2312424,"uid":325118,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T03:26:34.000Z","msg":"群雞起舞，我要幾十個老雞服侍我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2